      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start, the tone is definitely right. However, I think it's a bit too brief for a full training module. We probably need more substance so people actually walk away with practical advice.\n\nCould you expand this into a more detailed guide? Maybe break it down into specific sections like \"Communication,\" \"Physical Space,\" and \"Conflict Resolution.\" Also, try to make sure the \"robustness\" score is solid—if the audit comes back too low on those keywords, the compliance team will flag it for a rewrite, which is a huge pain for me. Just please keep it helpful and don't let the keywords take over the actual meaning.",
